106
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,850
Tuan Preechapiban.

107
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:49,360
Apakah kamu akan mengakui kesalahanmu?

108
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:53,720
Prinsip-prinsip Hukum menetapkan bahwa

109
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:58,200
