130
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:05,880
Klao yang terhormat.

131
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:10,280
Mari ikut saya.

132
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:20,880
Saya harus pamit sekarang, Bibi.

133
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,010
Astaga!

134
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,560
Ketika Guru Klao menghilang,

135
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:58,080
Kondisi fisik Lord Phop
