179
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,420
Pop...

180
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:34,860
Bangkitlah, kumohon.

181
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,120
Klao yang terhormat, mohon bangun.

182
00:17:46,890 --> 00:17:51,280
Kita tidak bisa hanya mengikuti keinginan
hati sendiri dalam setiap hal, Phop.

183
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:55,020
Jalan seperti itu akan membawa kehancuran bagi hidupmu.

184
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:58,200
Benar sekali, Romo.

185
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,100
Inilah hidupku.

186
